{
  "logNo": "224223160258",
  "title": "노화, 노화에 따른 근감소증(Sarcopenia)",
  "addDate": "2026. 3. 20.",
  "categoryNo": "32",
  "parentCategoryNo": "32",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=224223160258",
  "html_size": 212058,
  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c2d91b57-0e53-4703-9c08-36d0e093543e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4d887257-050c-4647-8361-e425e42806fd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8c53a75d-dc55-4fbe-ac3b-b46850bdb2fe\">&quot;노화&quot;가 무언지는 누구나 알고 있다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c3831517-1ce8-4941-9938-f18ec5c8842e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dde1b1c1-9f89-4674-9aef-77731daa5884\">아니. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-42a44fe3-b094-4b15-a8e5-b1d51df60c49\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-36d17d07-8875-4451-8a8f-0dafe00b8927\">노화, 즉 늙어간다는 것이 어떠한 것인지를 알고 있다고 생각한다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c1461d9f-81b4-452c-b71e-f487a2a3ccef\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7a488132-e142-40b9-834b-670ab6c56c21\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f3339958-8154-4cfc-8659-6a305f65c41b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5b1ec85f-344f-46c2-b411-81452a35bc3e\">그러나 노화의 &#x27;정의&#x27;를 명확히 아는 사람은 드물다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1dfe9688-f025-49dc-9255-a5e54b216a9b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-37306ffc-5174-47ba-a017-a874b2fac79e\">그래서 노화가 무언지 알고 있다고 생각하는 사람도 노화를 설명하기가 쉽지 않을 것이다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d6a57113-873e-41bf-8373-696367328ee9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-300e5729-03d9-4bd0-80cf-94933c303e99\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-c2d91b57-0e53-4703-9c08-36d0e093543e\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-96ae372f-48ad-4af3-884a-4461f2d189e4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:259px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-96ae372f-48ad-4af3-884a-4461f2d189e4\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fcc696ac9d3bdfff.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"259\", \"originalHeight\" : \"194\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"111489\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fcc696ac9d3bdfff.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/fcc696ac9d3bdfff.png\" data-width=\"259\" data-height=\"194\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-96ae372f-48ad-4af3-884a-4461f2d189e4\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\", \"fileSize\": \"111489\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-4df19f48-7b70-4e3e-baf1-4c8f9c85b410\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-281d4df1-048a-4f64-a44c-911111acb29a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e1eaba85-2cf1-442a-8519-0b34178c5861\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-61d9ebe1-8fc1-4968-b5aa-8b3e4ed564f2\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a3b5cf02-42a4-4405-9a0e-f10581b57e9c\"><b>광의의 노화(aging)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-bbf60966-876e-40ca-b928-c87e27efd100\">는 생물체가 수태된 순간부터 사망까지 배아, 성숙, 성년기의 모든 변화를 의미한다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d5fcdc54-79f7-4e24-8bf9-4b7ea2ea1268\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ae81798b-b905-4e65-a139-31712c27f132\"><b>협의의 노화(aging, senescence)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-41d90fdd-2ca5-4edc-95b6-68be8a7903c5\">는 성숙한 다음부터를 지칭하며 시간이 갈수록 비가역적으로 나빠져 사망 확률이 높아지는 과정을 말한다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d1a45dce-e6e5-4557-8fab-d695bc29ffed\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2b1e5453-8237-48cd-942a-a5a63281850a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d8cc8379-2325-413b-ab6f-08a0b6a9dda6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d0b9ec88-356d-4f92-93ca-96d85dd5f93f\">세게보건기구(WHO)에서는 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ed83dfe4-7186-4a30-889e-72d5ea9fcc04\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f263cf74-08cd-403c-ba85-ab99e3365936\"><b>&quot;생물학적 수준에서 노화는 시간이 지남에 따라 다양한 분자 및 세포 손상이 축적되는 과정이다. 이는 신체적, 정신적 능력의 점진적인 감소와 질병 위험의 증가, 그리고 궁극적인 사망을 초래한다</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-68f42be4-9893-436c-ba59-633d6c89a3f7\">&quot;</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1990a6e8-9ad7-4012-be3e-75d3eec03e09\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-aeda9afb-0137-45af-bec4-1c32fd776cc0\">라고 설명하고 있다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-1140257a-f25a-4904-8e13-0d3a61f2be4a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-5c51c927-b8f1-43bf-94bf-610172679800\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-96f5f758-3183-4a12-ad99-dd6947c81de7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d0ca9652-dd5d-4a99-a5b0-f86618ba5995\">그래서 노화는 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-18a94d2d-96df-4a0d-bc30-06ebc81e433c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1e7064ff-3a53-4cd4-87a1-92531fba43b3\">1. 생리적 기능의 감소</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-20ac62db-0cdd-469e-b12e-4114f30388d0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-44257f7a-c037-45bc-a7d1-60bc0dbcfbba\">2. 질병에 대한 감수성 증가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4570076b-4b88-4377-b98c-792d2a66f581\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6c121a75-3de0-478d-aeda-7028bf3b26be\">3. 환경적 스트레스에 대한 적응능력 감소</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-906db618-a815-4e65-935c-33cb566955fe\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-784af52b-4678-4bbc-95bc-967674f2a997\">가 동반된다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-cb00f51d-01c5-42ca-9e3b-b08a317b23e6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2c824107-2d97-4491-ab06-cb5af6adcc6d\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-257b5a75-9c3a-45a6-89b4-f8e8333ddc24\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-486cdc87-62c1-4d8f-93ba-2e766b0b2567\">나이가 들어감에 따라 매년 평균 2% 정도의 생리학적인 시스템의 감소가 일어난다고 한다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0368735e-8918-4889-b6e7-c0ba7a8456f9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-73d1b131-0c26-466e-9bbb-fa2b3c5c3a11\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-78d8925e-70cd-4a68-b2d0-e59bb3124e2c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b8c838cb-7e56-4232-8f1d-dbaf44be8194\">이 과정은 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-fddd8171-452a-49da-831f-2ab47f35cdeb\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cc90d92b-025f-44b5-bce8-b0877a436c02\">1. 유전</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e9d842c6-3f4d-4950-92f0-0e408e7df697\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-29151907-6822-4876-ad81-297ee47ddbfa\">2. 생활습관</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-73668941-2498-4f50-93c4-0897d51c5a31\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f2060197-bd73-4e14-bc46-5d42cd962059\">3. 환경</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-7e82b1a9-c777-4dd9-a38c-a7f5736fd7a9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1086e035-a99b-473e-a56d-9b3ce3ebca5d\">이 관여하고, 이 중 유전은 30%에 못미치는 것으로 알려져 있다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f85b71af-a4af-4e03-94f3-4cd53f52f62d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-88490e34-5d4a-4af0-93ac-c8f67ba8d6c9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3c700f69-3261-44de-b39d-fb97d780e82d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0d6e5afd-d7d9-42ed-a931-2450fe99bc6b\">적절한 식이, 운동, 체질량 지수, 금연 등의 생활습관을 가진 사람이 그렇지 못한 사람들에 비해 10년 더 수명이 길다는 연구가 있었다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e55161a2-b44a-4047-bc40-ab7b1e570f77\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-00aa5944-a837-48f0-9679-4386e92440ac\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6f0783f6-0460-455c-a862-b4a9828a4260\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-27777d82-b76c-4d4b-9544-a95b368766da\">질병의 조기검진과 예방조치, 의학의 발달, 사회 경제적 안정망 및 보건의료 체계가 더 향상된 환경에서는 더 많은 수명 연장을 이룰 수 있는 가능성이 있다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-605d3f40-8625-4c68-9cbb-d2801c630831\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-27e0040a-6eb4-4edd-85d6-b1ca350dea12\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-4df19f48-7b70-4e3e-baf1-4c8f9c85b410\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d04c3143-08b0-45a8-be54-7c226af668ef\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:275px;\">\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-d04c3143-08b0-45a8-be54-7c226af668ef\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3110e296177563b9.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"275\", \"originalHeight\" : \"183\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"78583\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3110e296177563b9.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/3110e296177563b9.png\" data-width=\"275\" data-height=\"183\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-d04c3143-08b0-45a8-be54-7c226af668ef\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\", \"fileSize\": \"78583\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-74366052-730e-480c-9b05-6fa98e692682\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ee1d0ba5-fcaa-4dd3-84d0-8ce7a5ac943f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f5497461-ee2c-4da3-bb7d-6a1a1619e5de\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8edb1701-cdea-4022-935e-d7d5868ffaf5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7bf62af1-f306-4a69-9133-3f7fc2a3805b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6e8422b4-5015-4218-b327-b4e0a2497117\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e5d256f1-8630-46ea-9866-366d50f5e2b9\">일반적으로 노화의 과정에서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9322ed46-52f3-48a4-8703-02c2ebc8ce72\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-8f852c61-f084-4c32-bdaa-f4d4546533cc\">심장은 약간 비대해지고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-57615942-ebfe-47b6-b1c1-1668b11c0ea1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-f994c543-06db-49cc-8a57-49fca8eed8a7\">운동시 최대 산소소비량은 10년마다 남자는 10%, 여자는 7.5% 감소하며</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-a5db6787-4590-4324-b06e-f1a745976465\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9e4177f5-c323-4c18-81ee-446ecb7ba955\">심박출량은 변하지 않는다</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5b70f812-79f9-4226-88ae-d7ad5d48aa65\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-45709d40-3af0-41c9-b577-86475e90a524\">폐의 최대 호흡능력은 20세에서 70세가 되는 사이에 40%나 감소한다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-eee4500a-e497-4ecc-9bfa-045eb2e3a95b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2a832b31-5f58-4f42-b26e-279559f0fea8\">뇌는 나이가 들면서 신경세포의 수가 감소하나 연결(시냅스 synapse)증가로 보상한다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-51e91c24-5e15-478f-9f0d-b165ece73baa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-141bbe32-3dfa-46cf-a0b8-de02eb9c6950\">신장 기능은 점차 떨어지고 방광 용적도 줄며 조직 위축에 따른 요실금이 증가한다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c3f75563-a79a-49aa-966c-60345a1c89f4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-eee44766-d020-4049-8fea-2e3dc83fd19b\">체지방은 소실되지 않고 오히려 늘게 되며, 축적 부위가 재분포되어 인체 심부로 이동하여 여자는 엉덩이와 대퇴부, 남자는 복부에 축적된다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c2039742-81a0-481a-91de-f5d4f174016f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a83abe48-ebcd-480e-9ad4-4b9a08fc6899\">시력과 청력이 감소한다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-32342221-39c6-4cda-8739-876e9a22ed48\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2d79c70a-38f6-40aa-a0a1-cde1443823a9\">근육량은 운동을 하지 않으면 30세에서 70세 사이에 20% 가량 감소한다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e9bc4823-c444-4bcd-86b8-a256bd25e5f9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-34bc7ea9-6b8d-4c81-b1d2-31bfa0c2661b\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4b3ff6d5-b73d-43dc-b609-535ae9a1a453\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ace5fc82-1ded-48ab-88bd-2ecc2e00b859\">특히나 50세에서 75세 사이에는 약 25% 정도의 근육량이 감소할 정도로 빠르게 근육 소실이 일어난다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-976bdd5d-8ece-4661-b1cb-cd58da56634b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dd4f5c4c-d925-44fb-84f2-7f3671e7c28e\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-74366052-730e-480c-9b05-6fa98e692682\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-036074cd-d63a-42f5-bf19-7fa45f760de4\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-036074cd-d63a-42f5-bf19-7fa45f760de4\", \"src\" : \"https://media.springernature.com/lw685/springer-static/image/art%3A10.1038%2Fs41574-021-00626-7/MediaObjects/41574_2021_626_Fig2_HTML.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"685\", \"originalHeight\" : \"595\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\", \"fileSize\": \"0\" }'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://media.springernature.com/lw685/springer-static/image/art%3A10.1038%2Fs41574-021-00626-7/MediaObjects/41574_2021_626_Fig2_HTML.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-036074cd-d63a-42f5-bf19-7fa45f760de4\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\", \"fileSize\": \"0\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-364527d0-a7bc-4b1e-9d92-54e179b4a47a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3b47a027-66ed-4306-8e10-f02d42d2e0d1\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4d6127bb-5fc3-4cea-a23a-f7d45249e995\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-95ab34a2-639c-4c2b-a6e5-daec621a9788\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-052379a1-ae46-4a41-a58b-00f0d8e0219b\"> Muscle mass index[muscle mass(kg)/height(m2)]를 이용하여 근육감소증을 정의</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4b6609cb-b29c-4990-a43c-1e37abdee5b0\">할 경우 (</span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-d08ff21e-3d2c-4fe2-8943-efcb4706b5dd\">남성 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-89d1f142-5e8a-425d-a5f8-d20f93ae66ba\"><b>&lt;7.0kg/m²</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-9f1d439a-5e35-4664-9d32-d328323ca739\">, 여성 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0700ac3c-a138-46cf-966f-3db4fb306b67\"><b>&lt;5.7kg/m²)</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs13 se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-23d21b31-20cd-4b30-bdd5-f375b7532723\"> 70세 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-18ba63b4-391a-4383-9bd4-a88720444397\">이하에서 10-25%의 사람들이 근육감소증에 해당하며, 80세 이상에서는 30%이상의 여자와 50%이상의 남자들이 근육감소증에 해당하게 된다. </span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8edb4674-7496-4f06-b8c9-22ca8225fd59\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-43eab7d1-87b7-4762-8b06-185aa84e1cb3\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-62e284fd-ea1c-456e-9451-e00d81089671\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b9332653-842f-420d-a826-6c96323fbd9e\">노화, 질병, 외상외에도 부적절한(보통은 부족한) 아미노산(단백질)의 섭취는 단백질 합성률을 저하시키고 결국에는 근육감소증의 발병을 촉진한다. </span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8e09b6c2-3901-4e02-b095-7723b7ea80c5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-08dc1335-2388-47ea-9788-2412e11cd6b1\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-727df8e5-3443-4ae7-bbe2-f237786a752e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-678eef3c-5a72-4b6e-8a68-8fe9aaf5224b\">근육은 끊임없이 근육단백질을 아미노산으로 전환, 분해시키기 때문에, 근육양을 유지하기 위해서는 단백질 합성률이  아미노산으로의 분해율과 균형을 이루어야 한다. </span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ca7d27d5-9f9a-4989-b9b3-bce6c10f64de\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3b64eaef-232b-48f9-ba04-84b4baeaa4c3\">근감소증이 발생하기 위해서는 수 년간에 걸친 합성과 분해의 불균형이 필요하며,적절히 단백질을 섭취하지 않는다면 합성보다 분해가 많아지고 그 결과로 근육양의 유의한 소실이 발생한다. </span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5238f257-830c-4aaf-977b-99100189367c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-1fd5d773-27d9-4db6-b2f2-066920e5d6c5\">노화에 따른 근육의 감소율은 매년 거의 1-2% 정도로 지속된다. </span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-743ba2e9-6e42-41c3-81be-4bedfd8e56d0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-4daccea8-036d-4d6c-b591-b76e165bbe10\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-e8e6da64-354b-4a32-987e-4e0b173ec8b0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2bcffa2c-b26f-4826-8d44-836348e5cb80\">그러기에 근육의 감소를 막기 위해서는 </span></p><ol class=\"se-text-list se-text-list-type-decimal\"><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f2ae3402-89ea-4e3d-b44a-834c4373da11\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-0cc4f75e-426b-4245-b4a3-dae364af5caa\">적절하고 충분한 단백질 섭취</span></p></li><li class=\"se-text-list-item\" ><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-10028e0d-31c4-435f-9efc-69a3da4e8fb0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-dfcf5db8-a49d-4ace-b59e-d6d3a3ae85ad\">근육 단백질 합성을 촉진하기 위한 운동</span></p></li></ol><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4a3163a2-cdc7-430c-bcc0-98d19c5a5218\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-23ea713c-10c0-4072-8c28-d91092596d62\">이 필수라 하겠다. </span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-649270f7-5bff-44a1-833e-5d0be5118f43\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7294aebc-e15c-4406-beb8-1a4d9671e8a5\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b53030cd-25f8-4e18-8e7b-533d7aaef79b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-a865b152-0da9-4802-8b03-42de0ac75565\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-54bf3768-589d-4f46-a02f-46db7efae087\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-e069ebc6-f050-4af0-8f2c-311c16dfe365\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3e87f13c-33dc-4357-869f-ea49a666128d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-53a652b3-6f50-4460-a998-883819055699\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-eec3a44e-3fdf-4c4a-b43b-75e31ee54e48\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-3a766b04-9b9d-463f-90d0-5573ffe99bba\">근육감소증(근감소증 Sarcopenia)의 예방을 위한 영양과 운동에 대해서는 다음 포스팅에서 소개하도록 하겠습니다. </span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-c96ddcad-92ca-4cde-b84d-6a5189731990\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-6aad407b-b426-4ae8-98ae-93d82a638e13\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-47a83c66-bce2-43fc-b65d-470aa4cd6a75\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-cabc3e81-3136-43db-92eb-906f7fb98e8f\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b7388168-c10b-469c-9c1d-207b61769c6e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-87c0de7c-1ee0-4230-81c6-29bcbe4744c1\">​</span></p><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8f80a45e-c089-4c67-aed8-171db63f919b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ca3db513-9035-45af-8ff1-5b9ee3e3fd1a\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-364527d0-a7bc-4b1e-9d92-54e179b4a47a\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-oglink se-l-large_image\" id=\"SE-0361ea6d-20d7-417c-aff1-a7b2f825436a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-oglink se-l-large_image se-section-align-\">\n                            <div clas